item.title: What is this site?
item.author: mail@eucalypto.net (Viktor Papara)
item.description: Hi there! You must be really curious to view this about page, I like that! So I’m Viktor Papara and write here about my experience with computers. Are you interested in my code? Than head over to my Github. Using Twitter? I’m also on Twitter.
